text: Own a piece of Glacier history, it's been 20 years since this little rustic GEM has been on the market. Located in the sought after Snowline Community! This 2 bedrooms with smaller flex room, is ready for your personal touches! Large beautiful deck to enjoy the outdoors! Some of the amenities include gated entry, outdoor pool, tennis courts, fishing pond, playground, walking trails, community clubhouse & for year round recreation. Currently a part time vacation rental, the opportunity exists to continue using the home as an income earning property. Your own cozy place to make memories! 20 mins to Mt. Baker, and 15 to Silver Lake!

Welcome to The Ridge in Blaine! This stunning new home offers 4 bedrooms and backs up to a serene greenbelt, ensuring privacy and a beautiful natural view. The covered outdoor living area in the back is perfect for year-round enjoyment. The main level features a spacious primary bedroom, and there's a flexible room ideal for a home office or den. The open and functional floorplan includes a bonus room, providing extra space to suit your lifestyle needs. Designed for modern, low-maintenance living, this home boasts luxury vinyl flooring, quartz countertops, and a slab-on-grade foundation. Conveniently located near downtown Blaine and I-5. $5, 000 Buyer Credit is available with our preferred lender, Becky Farrar at Evergreen Home Loans.

Discover unparalleled coastal living! This uniquely situated home enjoys 100' of exceptional low-bank waterfront and panoramic views, including majestic Mount Baker, Birch Bay, and the San Juan Islands. Within the gated Birch Bay Village, walk next door to a quiet park/playground and marina. An active clubhouse, pool, and private golf course are just a bike ride down the lane. The ground floor sports 2 garages, 2 bedrooms, hobby room, and an open-plan lounge/dining/gourmet kitchen. Upstairs boasts a master suite, 4th bedroom, and private rooftop deck. The solarium and spacious outdoor areas are perfect for entertaining or enjoying the serene surroundings. With a few stairs leading to the beach, this home is truly one of a kind.

Discover the perfect blend of modern comfort & seclusion. This beautiful 2-story 3+ bedrm, 2.5 bath home boasts ample indoor & outdoor living space on 3.2 acres. Garden space, trails, seasonal creek & pond, a nature lovers paradise. Main floor features a modern kitchen w/ granite counters, dining area, living rm, office/library, 1/2 bath & mudrm w/ access to 2-car garage. Upstairs, 3 bedrms, including a primary suite w/ an en-suite bathrm & WIC, 2 bonus rms, spacious landing & laundry. Enjoy year-round comfort w/ A/C & plentiful upgrades including brand new carpet throughout! 2 mins from public lake access & boat launch. Conveniently located near Bellingham & Burlington, & 10 mins from I5, this property combines privacy w/ accessibility.

2.99% assumable loan for VA buyers! Timeless and thoughtful, this single-level home in an established Lynden neighborhood is designed for both comfort & luxury. The primary suite is a true retreat, complete with sitting area, deluxe walk-in closet, heated marble floors, jetted tub, & bath side fireplace. Every detail has been considered in the many updates throughout. Exposed beams & craftsman touches add classic style, while skylights & solar tubes give this home a light, bright feel. Entertaining is easy with open kitchen, two living spaces, and vinyl plank flooring throughout. Enjoy the mature landscape in the large, fenced backyard from the deck, or retreat indoors to the A/C. Home backs to a park and is wired for generator. Perfection!

Birch Bay Village 2018 4 bedroom home with 2 & 3/4 baths and 2, 213 sq. feet of living space. Stainless steel appliances, and granite countertops. Samsung front loading washer and dryer stay. 5 mini split heat/air conditioning units to keep you warm in the winter and cool in the summer. Primary on the main floor with walk in closet and ensuite. One other bedroom down and two more bedrooms upstairs with full bath. The back yard is fenced and pet ready. Located across the street from Kwann Lake and within walking distance of the pool and clubhouse. Village amenities include a 9 hole golf course with snack bar, marina, salt water parks, beaches, tennis and pickleball courts, club house, pool, 2 man made lakes and 24 hour manned gated security.

The Sunnyland charmer you've been waiting for! This light & bright single level craftsman has been tastefully updated and could not be more perfect! Centrally located and walking distance to your favorite restaurants, breweries, Trader Joes & more! Just wait until you see this primary bedroom with vaulted ceilings & en-suite bathroom. New hardwood floors, paint, counters & more make this home move in ready. The fully fenced, full sun yard is low maintenance but has mature fruit trees, garden beds and even a chicken coop! 2 small storage spaces for all your tools & toys. Property has received amazing short term rental income that could continue or be used as your next home!

Must see this serene and inviting home! Extensively updated in 2024, this stunning Skeers home backs onto Galbraith Mountains bike trails and features thoughtful interior design notes with quality materials. Short walk to Whatcom Falls Park! Features a 2024 roof, new solid cherry hardwood floors, a new kitchen, and more. Open kitchen/living plan perfect for entertaining. The spacious primary bedroom is on the main level with a private bath, free tub, dual shower, walk-in closet. Upstairs, find two additional bedrooms, a full bath, and an open loft area perfect for an office, music room, or home workspace. The private, beautifully landscaped backyard has no homes behind it. Modern home, surrounded by nature, close to town. Unmissable!

Single level condo with garage sits on the 5th green, enjoy the outdoor beauty of this unique end unit with views of the golf course, ponds, Mt. Baker/surrounding mountains, and sunrises. Vaulted ceilings w/picture windows flood the living space with natural light. This 2 bed 2 bath home has air-conditioning for complete comfort, beautiful gas fireplace, master bath has a jetted tub w/separate walk-in shower. Nice attached garage for easy parking and storage. Brand new luxury vinyl plank in LV room, dining, hallway, kitchen, and guest bath as well brand new carpet in both bedrooms. Sit on the deck or spread out to the adjacent grassy green space! Close to everything, this is easy living at its finest!

Welcome to this affordable, well-maintained 3 bedroom/1.75 bath home. With lots of natural light and a great floor plan, this home features a large cozy living room with hardwood floors and a free-standing stove, large bedrooms with newer vinyl plank and laminate flooring, primary with ensuite, office, jetted tub in main bath, carport, and a large detached bonus area. The large level fenced in backyard with garden space is just waiting for you to create your own private oasis. Close to the local elementary school and nearby trails, this home is only 30 minutes to Bellingham and close to the Canadian border. Not in the flood zone. Why rent when you can own this lovely home with endless opportunities!

A rare find so close to town and the US/CAN border, located directly next to hundreds of acres of protected forest land that insures continued privacy. 2.46 acres, over 2700 Sq Ft of living space. Home has the Northwest Contemporary feel . 4 bedrooms with 4 full baths, 3 of 4 rooms are suites. Comfortable Living room, large bonus room upstairs with Vaulted ceiling, both overlooking the beautiful wooded areas, two pellet stoves and 2 mini split heat pumps keep you warm in winter and cool in summer, freshly painted inside, newer appliances. High speed internet. Large shop is insulated, high bay doors, sheet rocked, bathroom, separate septic & electric meter, all set up to finish off the accessory dwelling unit. Many more upgrades.

This custom, one-owner home is your perfect retreat just minutes from the City. 5+ acres w/ 3 bdrms, +a den, and 2.5 bthrms, it offers modern comfort and rustic charm. Located at the end of a dead-end road and a long private driveway, the property features an oversized two-car garage, a 30x40 shop with 100amp service, a generator & RV hookup, and a circle driveway. Enjoy a serene setting on your large covered patio, located just off the chef's kitchen with a huge island to gather, perfect for entertaining. You will appreciate the wrap-around deck, Vaulted ceilings, A/C, 2-story foyer, orchard, garden, and tree-lined backdrop. Relax in the hot tub under the stars in complete privacy. Youre just 10 minutes from shopping, restaurants and I-5.

This is a spacious home of 3 beds that is privately situated at the end of a lane/alley surrounded by open space lawn and looks out to a wooded area in Malloy Village. This community is very unique and has a clubhouse, playgrounds, and a community orchard. It is a very popular walking area too. The floorplan is open, spacious, and efficient with large rooms, and all the appliances remain (the range is brand new). In this development, invisible fences are allowed, but no real fences may be placed as the HOA dues of $145 per month cover all the landscape and mowing maintenance, and access is needed for that. There are no rental restrictions and this was rented for $2, 650 per month.

Like new and move in ready. This 2020 built 3 bed 1.75 bath rambler is located in a nice neighborhood with other newer homes. Boasting fantastic mountain views, sizable spacious lot, covered front porch, oversized garage, and a gated & fully fenced backyard w/a backdrop of mature trees. Inside, an open concept floor plan with engineered plank flooring, upgraded kitchen cabinets, stainless appliances, recessed lighting, & a ductless heating & cooling system for those hot summer days. The spacious bathrooms have beautiful ceramic tile flooring & solid surface countertops. The owners suite has its own full bath, walk-in closet, and a large sliding glass door that leads you to your outdoor patio & spacious backyard. Come and take a look today!

Don't miss out on the opportunity to live in one of Bellingham's finest 55+ condos in the heart of the Cordata neighborhood. This incredible 2bd/1.75ba ground level home is located in the El Dorado community and offers radiant floor heating, gas fireplace, patio off living area, stainless appliances, granite counters and more! Enjoy the convenience of a single car garage, a clubhouse with 2 furnished rentable units for guests, a dog run and a community garden with a greenhouse all just steps away from this remarkable condo. El Dorado is secure, pet friendly and close to shopping, trails and parks. This is a lifestyle you deserve.

This Lettered Streets condo embodies the essence of urban living, offering convenience and efficiency in a prime location. Thoughtfully designed to maximize privacy and comfort. Newly remodeled! Spacious kitchen for culinary enthusiasts. Light filled interiors with tall ceilings and a wall of windows offers views of nature and greenery. Private patio that overlooks Maritime Park and steps away from Bellinghams Trails. Secure underground parking. Situated in a vibrant community, enjoy easy access to a plethora of dining, shopping, the Waterfront/Harbor with entertainment options. Whether you are a first-time buyer, a savvy investor, or someone looking for a pied--terre in the heart of the city, this property is sure to impress.

Pride of ownership is evident in this impeccable home at the Reserve at Cordata. Lovely two story, three bedrooms with primary bedroom on main level, two car garage, low maintenance front yard. New furnace and air conditioner, washer, dryer, microwave, carpet, new floor in utility room Solar energy for greatly reduced monthly PSE bills. Home backs up to lush greenbelt for privacy while sitting on the deck in the fully fenced back yard. Storage building in back yard and gas plumbed at the outdoor patio. Ready for you to move in!

Welcome to 3806 Bennett Ave in Bellingham, a charming 2-story home boasting 1, 846 square feet of living space. This home features 3 bedrooms and 2.25 bathrooms. The lower level includes a cozy family room, perfect for entertaining or relaxing. To add to this well-rounded house is A/C, tankless water heater, updated kitchen and dining room, new paint, and attached 2 car garage. Outside, the fully fenced yard is complete with a dedicated dog run for your furry friends. Mountain views are see from many windows. Sidewalks and nearby parks allow for recreational opportunities. This home offers an ideal blend of comfort, style, and location, making it a perfect choice for your next move. Don't miss the chance to make this beautiful home yours!
This bright and airy waterfront condominium has a pool, private beach, fantastic views of the Salish Sea and is located right next to the Point Roberts Marina. Affordable waterfront living.

3 BEDROOM RAMBLER - BLAINE. Vaulted ceiling in living area, open design in kitchen, dinning and living room. Quartz counter-tops, kitchen pantry and and Island counter. Master bedroom with a walk in closet. Full appliance package included. 3 bedrooms with 2 full baths. Large 8600 Square Foot lot, fully fenced, fruit trees and landscaping. Double garage and lots of paved parking. Great Location.

One of the very few unbuilt lots available ready to get started in Anderson Park. Paved Street, curbs, sidewalk and all utilities are at property in the street. This 6, 700 square foot lot is level at the end of Sagebrush Lane. Homes on either side are constructed. Very sharp price for your opportunity.

Stunning Waterfront, Marin Condo, overlooking Semiahmoo Bay & White Rock BC. Beautifully designed open concept condo w/luxury finishes throughout. Gourmet kitchen, SS appliances, granite counters, large island, wine bar & dining area. Gorgeous living room with gas fireplace and spectacular Bay & Island views. Radiant floors throughout. Step out to a large patio & steps to the beach. Primary bedroom with walk-in closet, granite counters, double sinks, glassed-in shower & separate tub. 2nd bedroom has private ensuite with a walk-in closet, plus a den. Private parking space and a storage room in the secured garage. Reserved parking space outside! Amazing condo is a minute's walk to Semiahmoo Hotel, Restaurants & Marina.

Embrace the beauty of nature on this exceptional 5-acre property, attractively priced for a swift sale. Nestled within a grove of trees, this picturesque oasis offers a level terrain that's ready to accommodate your vision, whether it's a cozy retreat or a grand residence. The property boasts a shared well, providing both convenience and sustainability for your water needs. Imagine the ease of having this essential resource readily available as you design and build your dream haven. Strategically positioned between Maple Falls and Sumas you'll relish the tranquility of rural living and still being connected to urban amenities. Located minutes from Silver Lake Park where you can enjoy hiking, camping, and fishing. This one won't last long!

Breathtaking Chuckanut Bay and Island views from this exquisite contemporary design by Alexei Ford. Perched on an expansive 1.88 ac private lot, bask in the west facing sun-filled interior and marvel at the custom cabinetry and live edge shelving by premier NW furniture designer Al Rosen. Situated just below MP 7.5 on the interurban trail, this is your launch pad for all things Chuckanut - where the Cascades meet the sea! This home features a zero step entry, in floor radiant heat, cozy wood stove, vaulted ceilings with car-decking, solid fir doors, windows & trim. Open concept living and all beds & baths on the main. The loft space is the perfect den or TV room. Dont miss the sleeping nook and hatch to the rooftop! Your sanctuary awaits.

Beautiful, ground-floor condo overlooking a peaceful creek in the heart of Lynden. This 2-bedroom residence has nice wood finishes, seclusion, and convenient proximity to shops and restaurants. Enjoy the open floor plan with granite countertops, hardwood floors, stylish window treatments, gas fireplace and picturesque creek side views. The primary bedroom is complemented by a spacious bath and a walk-in closet. Unit comes with a single-car garage with an additional undercover parking spot. Step out to the private backyard patio and take in what nature has to offer.

Boasting a sensational south-facing view of the Cascade foothills, this property offers all the details expected for luxurious living. Features include wide plank hickory hardwood floors, soaring 12-foot ceilings, air conditioning, stamped concrete, and Pental Quartz countertops. Enjoy the bonus/media room and a full tile shower with frameless glass, a rain head, and a soaker tub. The garage includes an electric car charger, epoxy-finished floors, and ample overhead storage. Outdoor living becomes an experience with the large covered patio, offering a peaceful, country-like ambiance that leaves a lasting impression.

Welcome to Crossridge Urban Community! Brand new single family homes that have been thoughtfully designed with architectural & community integrity, each home feels custom with its elevated finishes and interior design. The Arroyo model has all the living on main floor that extends out through modern French doors onto a large covered patio. Private backyard with 6' fence, gate, modern pavers, low maint turf and raised bed planters. Upstairs you'll find the primary with attached ensuite and fully tiled walk-in shower + 2 more bedrooms with an additional full bath. Don't forget the detached flex space with half bath accessed through garage that can be used as an office, family room, or for guests. Broker registration onsite.

Discover your dream home in Woodbine Estates! This impeccably maintained single-level home offers 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and an office, providing ample space for work and relaxation. Enjoy the seamless layout connecting the living room, kitchen, dining, and family room, perfect for entertaining. The updated kitchen boasts custom cabinets, SS appliances, granite countertops, gas range, eating bar, and under-cabinet lighting. Relax by the cozy fireplace, adding warmth and charm to the living space. This move-in-ready, low-maintenance home features fresh interior paint, a recently painted exterior, and a newer roof. Mature landscaping ensures privacy, while the location just outside city limits provides easy access to Lakeway and Lake Padden.

Welcome to this very private-feeling Sand Dollar Condo, close to all amenities of downtown. This end-unit has great privacy & edible blueberries landscaping. This convenient condo lives like a house with plenty of storage including attached garage w/ladder to attic. Theres a full kitchen, an open living & dining area with a sliding door to a back patio. Main floor has bedroom, bath & laundry rooms. Upstairs is the spacious bedroom ensuite. There is an open loft portion that facilitates light and circulation for comfortable heating & air conditioning from the energy efficient heat pump. The HOA is professionally managed and welcomes all ages and pets. WSG, recycling, & basic cable & internet utilities are included for total of $556 dues.

Pride of workmanship is here! Worry free living in a quality new 2 bed 2 bath & office rambler in a great location. Minutes to one of the nicest sandy beaches in WA state and 10 minutes from I-5 to the east. 4.5+ acres accessed on a non thru road which means a little peace and quiet with room to roam, garden, create, entertain and do what you do. Beautiful home with open floor plan, spacious kitchen with large island, stainless appliances, large ensuite in primary bedroom with walk in shower and closet. Enter from the two car garage thru the mud room with laundry to help keep things neat and orderly. Heat pump with mini splits for efficient heating and air conditioning. This home and grounds have what it takes to make a fantastic home life.

Beautiful 5 BR, home located on a quiet cul-de-sac with mature trees. Walking distance to parks and downtown shopping. 9 ceilings on both floors. Main floor primary BR with ensuite BA and tiled double shower. Additional powder room on the main. Four BRs, flex room with skylights, 1 bathrooms and plenty of storage on the second floor. Large great room with white oak engineered hardwood floors, kitchen with brand new Kitchen Aid appliances, granite countertops, large island and ample pantry storage. Spacious laundry room with washer/dryer. Garage with 12 door will accommodate RV or boat. Mini splits provide heat and AC on both floors. A large, covered patio will be great for entertaining. Easy ADU conversion in garage space.

BRAND NEW, quality built, 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home on a large lot! Features include luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, stainless appliances, quartz counter tops, tile backsplash, dual sinks in primary bathroom, mini-split unit that provides low cost heating with the benefits of A/C. Spacious kitchen with shaker style quality soft close cabinets and a nice patio off the dining area. Brand new 3 bedroom septic system! No HOA. Enjoy a brand new home about a 35 minute drive from Bellingham. Home is located way in the back of the development for low traffic. Huge sunny side yard perfect for a garden or a competitive game of badminton! Home is ready for move in. One year builder warranty and garage has plug for electric car charging!

Experience epic fun at Grand Bay condos and beach! Vibrant seaside-style resort life w/in golf cart zone w/nearby Birch Bay restaurants, Beach Cat Brewery, library, parks. Full time or second home. Full saltwater bay view, west facing top floor condo and deck w/elevators, outside entry. Fully turnkey. Stylish finishes, radiant floor heat in baths. 1, 058 SF, 2 BR, 2 full BA-separate bath and shower in primary. Built 2007. On site amenities-community hot tub, storage for kayaks, paddleboards & bikes. Association owns grass field by mouth of Terrell Creek & beach rights w/firepits in front. 2 pets OK. Dues inc. maintenance, insurance, garbage. Beach berm in front w/ 1.5 mile of level surface. Small boats in front Aug-Oct crabbing season OK.

Nestled on a generous, mature lot, this charming single-level home features 3 bedrooms plus a den and 1.75 baths, spanning 1368 sqft. Highlights include a 2-car garage, newer roof, kitchen and appliances, flooring and a spacious back deck ideal for entertaining, and a fully fenced yard for privacy. Perfect for enjoying comfortable living in a serene setting with ample outdoor space. Close to shopping, schools and parks.

Charming and spacious single-story condominium in a 55+ gated community, located on a quiet dead-end street. This well-maintained 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is ready for your personal touches. A new roof is scheduled, already included in the condo dues. The gated community which allows privacy and security, has low HOA dues. There is a clubhouse for those special occasions and lots of extra parking. Close to health services, shopping & more! Enjoy a serene and inviting environmentmake this lovely home yours today.

Charming 4Bdrm 2.5Bth home in a desirable neighborhood. Nestled on a quiet street, this home is just minutes away from all the amenities that Bellingham has to offer, yet feels like a serene retreat. Step inside to find a spacious living room, perfect for entertaining or relaxing with loved ones. The a lovely kitchen with a slider that opens up to your expansive deck, where you can enjoy morning coffee or evening BBQs in the privacy of your fenced-in yard. The dining room, which can also serve as a second living area, boasts a cozy gas fireplaceideal for chilly evenings. Outdoor enthusiasts will love being close to numerous trails and wooded areas for hiking & exploring. Dont miss the opportunity to make this exceptional home yours!

Great Bellingham location--the Cottages at Cordata--spacious, like new ground floor unit with a patio and private backyard. Assigned parking space close to the entrance with a private storage closet. A community storage closet is also an added feature. Great room with fireplace, 9 ft ceilings & open kitchen that are sure to please. Secure entrance with intercom access. Nicely maintained yard--2 bedrooms- 2 bathrooms & plenty of windows for natural light. Cordata location is one of the best for convenience, shopping, walkability, and parks nearby in the heart of WCC. A well-run HOA makes for a great investment property. New water heater & well-cared-for appliances--washer and dryer brand new! Easy care LVP & vinyl flooring. A must see.

Discover this stunning home in Gate Two of beautiful Sudden Valley! Meticulously cared for, it boasts pristine front and back landscaping, deer-protected gardens, berry bushes, and diverse plant life. Inside, enjoy soaring ceilings, a stone gas fireplace, and rich wood floors. Located close to all Sudden Valley amenities, it's within walking distance to Lake Louise and AM/PM Beach on Lake Whatcom. The primary bedroom features a spacious walk-in closet and a private balcony with breathtaking views. The huge two-car garage offers ample storage, and the roughed-in basement provides an additional 400 sq ft of storage space. Plus, the roof is only a year old! Must see to appreciate!

BUYER BONUS!!!This stunning 2-story Bayview floorplan features 4 beds & 3 full baths. Enjoy the spacious deck off the main living area and primary suite with breathtaking water views over Birch Bay. The primary suite is a true haven, boasting a lavish 5-piece ensuite with rain head shower, custom vanity, and oversized walk-in closet creating ample space for all your needs. The lower level includes a bonus room for the perfect guest suite. Luxury abounds with ceramic tiles, custom cabinets, and high-end appliances in the chef's dream kitchen. Proximity to golf clubs, Semiahmoo, Vancouver BC, and Seattle. Indulge in the epitome of elegance and coastal living. Your perfect oasis awaits.

Lovely 1-level home with NO STAIRS! Level lot with fully-fenced backyard. Covered patio! This 3 bedroom/2-bath home has lovely wood and tile floors, no carpet anywhere. Super convenient location, surrounded by other attractive homes on a tree-lined street with sidewalks. One-owner home is only 10 years old so has the benefits that come with newer homes, like central air-conditioning, newer stainless appliances, stone counters, and low wear & tear. This is a great alternative to a condo, with the low-maintenance yard and no HOA to deal with. Great floor plan has a unique and awesome butler's pantry with a wine cooler that you don't want to miss!

This large 5-bedroom home has space for everyone! It features open living areas, a main floor primary bedroom with an ensuite bath & walk in closet, soaring vaulted ceilings, a spacious kitchen with an island, hardwood oak flooring, large windows & skylights that flood the home with natural light, a spacious dining space, two large decks that are perfect for entertaining & has a two-car garage plus off-street parking. Air conditioning, a whole house generator & all new appliances were recently installed & the home is connected to natural gas. No dealing with propane! Easy access from Lake Whatcom Blvd. makes this a great location within the community. Come & enjoy all of the incredible amenities that Sudden Valley has to offer!

Fully remodeled, open & bright condo in beautiful Cordata! This fantastically laid out, 2nd floor unit has been completely updated with new & modern cabinetry, counters, appliances, bathrooms, flooring, paint, and the list goes on. Large great room with oversized kitchen island perfect for cooking and entertaining is open to living room with access to sunny balcony. Spacious primary bedroom offers a walk-in closet and generous bathroom suite with walk-in shower. Other unit features include one-car garage, kitchen pantry, and main floor laundry closet. This complex is beautifully landscaped, with sidewalks throughout and a park-like shared outdoor space.

Don't miss an opportunity to enjoy one of Bellingham's most stunning bay views with beach access. Located at the end of a non-through street, this 7, 000 plus square foot, highly detailed estate was custom built for the current owners and is situated on nearly an acre. Enjoy spectacular sunsets, city lights, endless views of the San Juan Islands, and one of the most beautiful yards and gardens imaginable. Features include a spacious open floor plan with 4 bedrooms, 6 baths, 2 offices, a cozy game room, and a primary suite with a spa-like bath. In addition, there is a separate living area, ideal for ultimate privacy for extended living or guests. The perfect location, seldom found, offering serenity from a busy life!

One of the largest cottages in Cordata Commons! Backyard faces permanent greenspace with great privacy. 1777 SF with primary bedroom on the main level with views into greenspace. Living room has vaulted ceilings and a gas fireplace. Upper level has office space plus 2 bedrooms and a full bath. Meticulous owners bought this house while still under construction, upgraded the interior and made beautiful improvements over the past 6 years. Kodiak is a dead-end street with access into community trails. Legally this is a condominium, but lives like a house. Community only shares storm water system, green spaces, trails and parks. Each owner owns their home and land individually.

Welcome to your dream home! This meticulously maintained, custom-built gem sits on 5 private wooded acres in the coveted Meridian School District. Enjoy a spacious 3-bedroom layout with two extra rooms or offices. The main floor boasts a primary bedroom with a large ensuite bathroom, walk-in closet, and attached flex room. Stay comfortable year-round with central air conditioning and cozy up by the wood stove on chilly nights. Outside, a 3-bay shop includes a heated and insulated workshop area, perfect for projects. The fenced backyard features fruit trees and ample space for gardening or play. Experience the perfect blend of quality, comfort, privacy, and convenience in this stunning property. Don't miss out-schedule a showing today

Upscale, penthouse water view condo in Barkley Village, with 2 lovely deck lookouts. Condo neighbors the Bellingham trail system, only moments from the cinema, multiple restaurants/pubs, banks, city library and fitness centers. Ultra-secure entry system, with gated private parking garage. Cozy master bedroom, with private balcony. Office in front area of well-designed, flowing home plan. Beautiful natural scenery from windows across the full view side; high ceilings. Granite countertops in generously broad kitchen, with appliances included. Separate shower/sitting tub in spacious bath. Bellingham offers unique proximity to the beaches and the mountains, only 1 hr. from Vancouver, BC. Investors, take note: No rental cap.

This beautiful 1923 South Hill charmer sits in a prime location with expansive views of Bellingham Bay. This home features over 2000 sq ft, with 3 bds and 2.5 baths. On the main floor, the gorgeous updated kitchen and living space open to a large deck. The private top-floor primary bedroom has a cozy built-in daybed and a deck with stunning views. While modern updates have been made throughout the home, the original charm is intact with striking fir trim, solid doors, and lots character. Updates include: electrical, plumbing, windows, and flooring. Landscaping provides privacy, plants deliver months of floral beauty & year-round birds. Minutes to Fairhaven, Boulevard Park & Taylor Dock.
neighborhoods: South Hill, South Hill Historic District

text: This property stands out as a hidden gem in Ferndale. Whether you're envisioning a private sanctuary or a space to cultivate your own piece of paradise, this property offers the canvas for your dreams. Live in the current residence while you build your dream home. The combination of stunning views, ample acreage, conveniently located right beside town, providing the perfect blend of rural charm and urban accessibility, making it a rare find in the real estate market. Currently in open space tax classification, buyer remove from classification if required.

Welcome to your piece of paradise! This remarkable nearly 7-acre parcel of vacant land is a blank canvas awaiting your vision. With a drilled well already in place and a boundary survey completed, you can rest assured that the groundwork has been laid for your dream home. This property offers breathtaking views of Lake Samish, creating a tranquil and idyllic setting that will undoubtedly captivate your senses. Tucked away in privacy and seclusion, providing a sense of peace and serenity that is hard to come by, this property promises to be the perfect escape from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. Make an appointment to view today!

PRICE REDUCED! May qualify for WSHFC Down Payment Assistance Prog. Seller will pay $2000 toward buyer closing costs. Spacious one bedroom condominium located on the South Hill, near Western, with seasonal views of Bellingham Bay. Building has an outdoor pool. Easily accessible to the South Bay Trail. Close to the Bellingham Farmer's Market and Boulevard Park. This unit comes with an enclosed deck off the living room so you can enjoy that morning coffee on your deck no matter what the weather is outside. Parking is assigned, covered and accessible below the unit. Low HOA fees are a bonus with this condominium. Comes with a separate storage unit. There's room to add a new euro-style washer/dryer combo machine and free on-site laundry.

Lake Padden Estates is an owner occupied 55+ community. Unit #43 is just right , not too big, not too small. This 2 bedroom, 1 3/4 bath home lives larger than its square footage with open living and dining areas and vaulted ceilings. Enjoy the private patio area that overlooks a lush green space behind the house. A convenient extra-long single car garage is attached. The house has been extremely well maintained and is move in ready. Residents of Lake Padden Estates have access to a community clubhouse, RV parking and trails. This development is across from Lake Padden Park and is a short drive to all that Bellingham has to offer!

Find quintessential Sudden Valley living in Gate 5, just off of Lake Louise Rd. Live in privacy, nestled among the trees! Living room has windows out to green space on two sides and a cozy rock fireplace. Kitchen features Brazilian cherry hardwood floors, maple cabinetry, and plenty of counter space.
